<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ntlafatso Foundation</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background: #006699;
      color: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      background: #004d66;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: #e6f2ff;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .section {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .section h2 {
      color: #006699;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .card-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    footer {
      background: #004d66;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background: #009933;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Ntlafatso Foundation</h1>
    <p>Ending Stigma. Empowering Lives. Building Healthier Communities.</p>
  </header>
  <nav>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#mission">Mission</a>
    <a href="#programs">Programs</a>
    <a href="#support">Get Involved</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Together We Fight Stigma</h1>
    <p>Learn how we're tackling stigma related to HIV/AIDS, Rare Diseases, Cancer, and Disabilities across Lesotho.</p>
    <a href="#programs" class="cta">Discover Our Programs</a>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="section">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Ntlafatso Foundation is a psychosocial health-based nonprofit founded in 2018 and registered with the Law Office of Lesotho. Our core commitment is to eliminate stigma around specific diseases and promote emotional, social, mental, and spiritual well-being.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="mission" class="section">
    <h2>Our Mission & Vision</h2>
    <p><strong>Mission:</strong> To eliminate stigma associated with diseases by fostering self-efficacy, social support, and spiritual resilience.</p>
    <p><strong>Vision:</strong> All individuals are empowered to live free from stigma and discrimination regardless of their health conditions.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="programs" class="section">
    <h2>Our Programs</h2>
    <div class="card-container">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Anti-Stigma Campaigns</h3>
        <p>Transforming mindsets and combating discrimination through community education and advocacy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Mentorship Program</h3>
        <p>Training future leaders in personal discovery and purpose-driven living.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Counselling Program</h3>
        <p>Support for caregivers, special groups, bereavement, and psychological healing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Transformational Talks</h3>
        <p>Inspiring sessions that motivate and empower individuals and communities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="support" class="section">
    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <p>Your support helps us reach more communities and eliminate stigma. Join us today.</p>
    <a href="mailto:ntlafatso2018@gmail.com" class="cta">Email Us to Get Involved</a>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="section">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:ntlafatso2018@gmail.com">ntlafatso2018@gmail.com</a></p>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> Quthing, Lesotho</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>Â© 2025 Ntlafatso Foundation. All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
